PE.PENALTIESFOR OH8PYL TYPE FARES CHANGES CHANGES NOT PERMITTED. CANCELLATIONS TICKET IS NON-REFUNDABLE. NOTE - ALL UNUTILIZED TAXES INCLUDING YR SHALL BE REFUNDED. SERVICE TAX -K3- GOODS AND SERVICE TAX SHALL BE REFUNDED. FLIGHTS WHERE THE CONNECTION TIME IS -UPTO 5 HRS OR NEXT AVAILABLE CONNECTION WHICHEVER IS LOWER ARE TO BE TREATED AS ONE FARE COMPONENT -FROM ORIGIN TO DESTINATION- AND IN CASE OF REFUND/CANCELLATION ALL UNUTILIZED TAXES INCLUDING INCLUDING YR SHALL BE REFUNDED. FOR RETURN TRAVEL PENALTY APPLICATION ON THE ABOVE ABOVE ITINERARIES SHALL BE PER FARE COMPONENT. PARTIAL CANCELLATION ON THIS ITINERARY SHALL NOT BE PERMITTED. FOR EXAMPLE WHILE HOLDING A TICKET FOR CONNECTION BOM DEL AMD OR VICE VERSA YOU SHALL NOT NOT BE ALLOWED TO CANCEL YOUR ONWARD OR RETURN FLIGHTS PARTIALLY AND MUST CANCEL THE ENTIRE ITINERARY OR TICKET. FARES WHEN COMBINED ON A HALF ROUND TRIP BASIS SHALL BE GOVERNED BY THE ORRESPONDING APPLICABLE TICKETED FARE PER SECTOR AND ITS APPLICABLE TERMS AND CONDITIONS NOTE- IF A NO SHOW TICKET IS PROCESSED ONLY TAXES WILL BE REFUNDED. NO CHARGE CANCELLATION OR AMENDMENT WITHIN 24 HOURS. YOU CAN CANCEL OR AMEND THE TICKET WITHOUT ANY ADDITIONAL CHARGES WITHIN 24 HOURS OF BOOKING THE TICKET. THIS FACILITY IS AVAILABLE UP TO 7 DAYS PRIOR TO THE SPECIFIED FLIGHT DEPARTURE ON THE FIRST LEG.
